# elaraSign Certificates Directory
# =================================
#
# ⚠️  THIS FOLDER SHOULD ALWAYS BE EMPTY  ⚠️
#
# ALL secrets exist ONLY in GCP Secret Manager:
#   - elarasign-master-key       (forensic decryption)
#   - elarasign-p12-certificate  (signing certificate)
#   - elarasign-p12-password     (certificate password)
#
# The setup script (npm run setup):
#   1. Generates secrets
#   2. Uploads to GCP Secret Manager
#   3. DELETES local copies
#
# This is intentional security - no secrets ever persist locally.
#
# For LOCAL DEVELOPMENT:
#   - Use Firebase emulators: firebase emulators:start
#   - App auto-generates temp certs when ELARASIGN_AUTO_GENERATE_CERT=true
#   - Or fetch secrets: gcloud secrets versions access latest --secret=NAME
#
# For PRODUCTION (Cloud Run):
#   - Secrets injected via --set-secrets in cloudbuild.yaml
#   - No files needed - all from environment variables
